Time To Event Dataset

ate.Rd

Time To Event Dataset

ate(ADSL, FUN = function(p) {     PARAMCD <- c("OS", "PFS")     PARAM <-
  c("Overall Survival", "Progression Free Survival")     data.frame(USUBJID
  = p$USUBJID, STUDYID = p$STUDYID, PARAMCD = PARAMCD, PARAM = PARAM, AVAL
  = vapply(PARAMCD, function(paramcd) {         switch(paramcd, OS =
  ifelse(p$ARM == "ARM A", rexp(1, 1/100), rexp(1, 1/80)), PFS =
  ifelse(p$ARM == "ARM A", rexp(1, 1/80), rexp(1, 1/65)))     },
  numeric(1)), AVALU = "MONTH", CNSR = sample(c(T, F), length(PARAMCD),
  replace = TRUE), stringsAsFactors = FALSE) }, ..., start_with)
